{"tid":1063380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天安門附近商場爆斬人案 距人民大會堂僅一地鐵站","createTime":"2019-03-15T17:15:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-15T17:47:48.000Z","uid":36901,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4439bb88f837b94923f0b23fd057cacd67999cb9","tid":1063380,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T17:15:41.000Z","msg":"【全國兩會】天安門附近商場爆斬人案 距人民大會堂僅一地鐵站<br />\n<br />\n3小時前<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全國兩會今早剛於北京閉幕，北京驚爆斬人案件。事件發生於今日下午2時40分許，地點為北京東城區東方新天地商場地下一層，事件中一名男子受傷。<br />\n<br />\n據北京市公安局東城分局官方微博@平安東城微博資料，25歲貴州梁姓男疑犯，持刀將另一名27歲黑龍江石姓男子劃傷。案發後，在商場保安協助下，梁男被附近執勤民警控制。傷者已被送往附近醫院治療，無生命危險。<br />\n<br />\n目前，案件正在進一步調查中。東城區東方新天地商場距離中國人民大會堂坐地鐵僅有一站之隔。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190315/59374079\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190315%2F59374079&d=hEl8YzVD%2FOsYsQiwoICJnITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=eb879fe9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190315%2F59374079&h=b817449c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190315/59374079</a>"},{"pid":"5b4c0cafefa39aeac7fd0dacd7fcb055d872af44","tid":1063380,"uid":21774,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T17:21:21.000Z","msg":"渣既<br />\n斬得一個"},{"pid":"c96b572a9d763a36daaa9e07ed7fceb9c5cdc452","tid":1063380,"uid":55581,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"5b4c0cafefa39aeac7fd0dacd7fcb055d872af44","tid":1063380,"uid":21774,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T17:21:21.000Z","msg":"渣既<br />\n斬得一個"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T17:31:57.000Z","msg":"又實名，成街天眼，一街便衣+解放軍，斬到一個已超標完成。如果做到今日單野既程度，直頭比人當神人咁拜。"},{"pid":"c56e9a2cf14facf5f181d8eda3e015d68289a5a3","tid":1063380,"uid":21774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c96b572a9d763a36daaa9e07ed7fceb9c5cdc452","tid":1063380,"uid":55581,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"5b4c0cafefa39aeac7fd0dacd7fcb055d872af44","tid":1063380,"uid":21774,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T17:21:21.000Z","msg":"渣既<br />\n斬得一個"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T17:31:57.000Z","msg":"又實名，成街天眼，一街便衣+解放軍，斬到一個已超標完成。如果做到今日單野既程度，直頭比人當神人咁拜。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T17:39:31.000Z","msg":"雙刀斬多件啦"},{"pid":"8769f355c2bcb58161e95f434f3e3b608b271053","tid":1063380,"uid":26752,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T17:47:48.000Z","msg":"人地四十幾件<br />\n你先得1件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}